<p class="">We won the Battle of Britain.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d24ef60b-5ea7-4fb3-b6f9-bff89d2e96a1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
