<p class="">We said the same in 1915 about the Liberal Government.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6f7a1f01-a6ba-48c9-a92a-8a67366f6cfb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
