                Mr. Rankin  (Glasgow, Tradeston)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dd4a5302-dfb0-4bd6-96f8-1e6d3b6b037b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
