<p class="">No, I will not give way again. I accept that those words <span id="479" class="column-number" data-column-number="479"></span> are not intended as an imputation of drunkenness. I think that people outside, when they read them, will put their own impression on them. I can only describe the statement as a vulgar and thoroughly unjustified observation which should not have been made by an hon. Gentleman in the responsible position occupied by a Parliamentary Private Secretary.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
