<p class="">Well, then, it is a pity, because it would have been a uniquely illuminating observation. We have to study and consider what is an act of aggression before we permit it to set in train what may prove to be a series of very grave events.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
