<p class="">Will the hon. Gentleman give way?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9e70dd72-616a-4d05-b5fc-f9280701249e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
