<p class="">The hon. Member for Hornsey (Mr. Gammans) seemed to be rather upset on two points. The first was that the party on this side of the House was not behind the Prime Minister. I just cannot imagine where he got that from—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-5d8ecea7-6ae0-400a-b4ae-e9cb83c39e95" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
