        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-0c117ea9-685a-44b6-9ea3-3a0f0f42449a">
                Mr. Eden
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0c117ea9-685a-44b6-9ea3-3a0f0f42449a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-14/debates/a7998b7e-2747-4f19-ba68-0d3f6fb5e1fd/(GovernmentPolicy)#contribution-0c117ea9-685a-44b6-9ea3-3a0f0f42449a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">My right hon. Friend has never regarded the 18 months as too little. His line has always been—[<em>Interruption.</em>] If I am incorrect, the right hon. Gentleman may correct my statement; please do not interrupt me. My right hon. Friend's line has always been fewer and longer.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0c117ea9-685a-44b6-9ea3-3a0f0f42449a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-14/debates/a7998b7e-2747-4f19-ba68-0d3f6fb5e1fd/(GovernmentPolicy)#contribution-0c117ea9-685a-44b6-9ea3-3a0f0f42449a">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
